Extra, extra—read all about it! 📰 iVueit proudly welcomes Satish M. as our new Director of Engineering.

Satish brings an unstoppable energy and a wealth of experience in building high-performing teams, driving groundbreaking software solutions, and scaling technology for maximum impact. His passion for innovation and disruption makes him the perfect addition to our team. 🦾

With Satish at the helm of our engineering efforts, iVueit’s future just got even more powerful. His expertise will ignite our next wave of innovation, driving us toward bigger, smarter, and bolder solutions. Excited for what’s ahead—welcome, Satish! ✅ #iVueit
